Package: origami
Type: Package
Title: origami - Cross-validation Framework
Version: 0.5
Date: 2014-08-17
Author: Jeremy Coyle <jeremyrcoyle@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Jeremy Coyle <jeremyrcoyle@gmail.com>
Description: origami provides a general framework for the application of
    cross-validation schemes to particular functions. By allowing arbitrary
    lists of results, origami accommodates a range of cross-validation
    applications. Some applications are implemented as examples.
License: GPL-3
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0),
    abind,
    plyr
Imports:
    SuperLearner,
    methods,
    foreach
Suggests:
    testthat,
    class,
    glmnet,
    data.table
